{
  "stem": "12756.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What they used to always tell me, when you got trouble, and the Germans come over, and I'm going to support you and let you  sleep  a few days, till you find another place.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember any name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because you see, after that-- just then he told me, he said, no, I couldn't tell you and keep you in my house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just here is a bush.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Go in the bush and hide in the bush for the time being.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "OK, I went to the bush.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the middle of the night, I heard coming some more people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was a run away from Kostopil, the people who were in a ring.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They run-- a lot was run away by seven, eight people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, the Jews with police, they took them together in one place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They don't let them out already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what I call a ring.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A circle, let's say.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sorry, maybe I said the wrong way-- in a circle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then it was already about 27 people came together to this bush.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was in the bush two before Rosh Hashanah, before Yom Kippur, when it started getting cold And farmers started-- you want to add more?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The farmers started threatening us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They say, we used to stay the night, digging potatoes from the farmers and eating through the day potatoes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the farmers tell us, if you're going to again steal potatoes, we'll call the Germans on you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we never stole them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we make a little meeting between us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were supposed to go from this place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In about 30 miles, it started big, long bushes-- about 100 miles bushes, tall ones-- not bushes, woods.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Woods.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we had to cross water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to go to our village.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
